iv></aside><main class="docMainContainer_TBSr"><div class="container padding-top--md padding-bottom--lg"><div class="row"><div class="col"><div class="docItemContainer_BWQo"><article><nav class="theme-doc-breadcrumbs breadcrumbsContainer_Z_bl" aria-label="Breadcrumbs"><ul class="breadcrumbs"><li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a aria-label="Home page" class="breadcrumbs__link" href="/api/"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="breadcrumbHomeIcon_YNFT"><path d="M10 19v-5h4v5c0 .55.45 1 1 1h3c.55 0 1-.45 1-1v-7h1.7c.46 0 .68-.57.33-.87L12.67 3.6c-.38-.34-.96-.34-1.34 0l-8.36 7.53c-.34.3-.13.87.33.87H5v7c0 .55.45 1 1 1h3c.55 0 1-.45 1-1z" fill="currentColor"></path></svg></a></li><li class="breadcrumbs__item"><span class="breadcrumbs__link">Futures REST API</span></li><li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a class="breadcrumbs__link" href="/api/docs/category/futures-api/charts"><span>Charts</span></a></li><li class="breadcrumbs__item breadcrumbs__item--active"><span class="breadcrumbs__link">Candles</span></li></ul></nav><div class="theme-doc-markdown markdown"><div class="row theme-api-markdown"><div class="col col--7 openapi-left-panel__container"><h1 class="openapi__heading">Market Candles</h1>
<pre class="openapi__method-endpoint"><span class="badge badge--primary">GET</span> <h2 class="openapi__method-endpoint-path">/:tick_type/:symbol/:resolution</h2></pre><div class="openapi__divider"></div>
<p>Candles for specified tick type, market, and resolution.</p>
<p>List of available tick types can be fetched from the <a href="#operation/tickTypes">tick types</a>
endpoint. List of available markets can be fetched from the <a href="#operation/symbols">markets</a>
endpoint. List of available resolutions can be fetched from the
<a href="#operation/resolutions">resolutions</a> endpoint.</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_LWe7 openapi-tabs__heading" id="request">Request<a href="#request" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Request" title="Direct link to Request">​</a></h2>
